data.description: Seller giving $10,000 to buy down interest rate pts. Envision a lovely, newer home on oversized lot, close to Juniper Lake Boat Launch; no HOA. Built in 2019, not in a flood zone equals very low insurance. In pristine condition, this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home is move in ready and runs on city water and sewer. A roomy retreat near highways and the city. Very ample back yard has a new green house, shed and patio. And there's still room to add a pool, jacuzzi, putting green and more. The split floor plan with large living room is perfect for entertaining. The spacious kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances, will delight any chef. Seller to assist with closing costs. Alarm system, survey and home warranty provided for peace of mind. Ideal for short or long term rentals. Welcome home.
